text: Dear @amandamilling, my sister is a paramedic fighting #Coronavirus on the front line. She started displaying symptoms on Friday and was tested Saturday. 5 days later and still no results - why? It’s no good boasting about 100,000 tests if you don’t deliver 100,000 results.
